OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1776953470
OL,3,CTrump extends US ceasefire with Iran
OL,4,Cbut says military blockade of ports
OL,5,Cremains
OL,7,FTrump made the announcement as
OL,8,Fceasefire talks looked increasingly
OL,9,Funcertain, with a two-week truce set
OL,10,Fto expire on Wednesday, as ITV News US
OL,11,FCorrespondent Dan Rivers reports
OL,13,FUS President Donald Trump has said
OL,14,Fhe's extending the ceasefire with Iran
OL,15,Fat Pakistan's request, as he waits for
OL,16,Fa "unified proposal" from Tehran.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
