PN,31702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1776953470
OL,3,CTrump extends US ceasefire with Iran
OL,4,Cbut says military blockade of ports
OL,5,Cremains
OL,7,FIn a post on Truth Social on Tuesday,
OL,8,FTrump also said the US military would
OL,9,Fcontinue its blockade of Iranian
OL,10,Fports, and claimed the Tehran regime
OL,11,Fwas "seriously fractured".
OL,13,FHe wrote: "I have therefore directed
OL,14,Four Military to continue the Blockade
OL,15,Fand, in all other respects, remain
OL,16,Fready and able, and will therefore
OL,17,Fextend the Ceasefire until such time
OL,18,Fas their proposal is submitted, and
OL,19,Fdiscussions are concluded, one way or
OL,20,Fthe other."
