OL,3,CTrump extends US ceasefire with Iran
OL,4,Cbut says military blockade of ports
OL,5,Cremains
OL,7,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,8,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,9,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,10,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,12,FThe extension comes as the deadline
OL,13,Floomed on the current fragile truce
OL,14,Fand proposed talks in Islamabad were
OL,15,Fput on hold, amid tensions over the
OL,16,Fongoing stand-off in the Strait of
OL,17,FHormuz.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
