OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1776953470
OL,3,CTrump extends US ceasefire with Iran
OL,4,Cbut says military blockade of ports
OL,5,Cremains
OL,7,FThe effective closure of the vital
OL,8,Fsupply route during the conflict has
OL,9,Finflicted a global economic shock and
OL,10,Fsent energy prices soaring.
OL,12,FPakistan's leaders, including Prime
OL,13,FMinister Shehbaz Sharif, had been
OL,14,Fmaking frantic efforts on Tuesday to
OL,15,Fget both sides to agree to further
OL,16,Fdiscussions.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
