PN,31705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1776953470
OL,3,CTrump extends US ceasefire with Iran
OL,4,Cbut says military blockade of ports
OL,5,Cremains
OL,7,FBut hopes faded as US Vice President
OL,8,FJD Vance, expected to again lead US
OL,9,Fnegotiators, called off a trip to
OL,10,FPakistan as Tehran refused to commit
OL,11,Fto attending.
OL,13,FThe White House said in a statement
OL,14,Fthat, in light of the president's
OL,15,Fannouncement, Vance and the US
OL,16,Fnegotiating delegation would not be
OL,17,Ftravelling to Pakistan on Tuesday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
