CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1776953470
OL,3,CTrump extends US ceasefire with Iran
OL,4,Cbut says military blockade of ports
OL,5,Cremains
OL,7,FSharif thanked the US president for
OL,8,Fextending the ceasefire with Iran,
OL,9,Fsaying it would allow ongoing
OL,10,Fdiplomatic efforts to proceed.
OL,12,FIn a post on X, Sharif said he was
OL,13,Fexpressing gratitude "on my personal
OL,14,Fbehalf and on behalf of Field Marshal
OL,15,FSyed Asim Munir" for Trump's "gracious
OL,16,Facceptance" of Pakistan's request to
OL,17,Fextend the ceasefire.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
