PN,31707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1776953470
OL,3,CTrump extends US ceasefire with Iran
OL,4,Cbut says military blockade of ports
OL,5,Cremains
OL,7,FSharif said he hoped both sides would
OL,8,Fcontinue observing the ceasefire and
OL,9,Freach a comprehensive peace deal
OL,10,Fduring the second round of talks
OL,11,Fscheduled in Islamabad, aimed at
OL,12,Fsecuring a permanent end to the
OL,13,Fconflict.
OL,15,FOnly earlier, Trump said he was ready
OL,16,Fto renew attacks against Iran if
OL,17,Fprogress was not made.
OL,19,FHe also told ITV News that "one way or
OL,20,Fanother", we're going to agree a deal
OL,21,Fwith Iran.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
