OL,3,CTrump extends US ceasefire with Iran
OL,4,Cbut says military blockade of ports
OL,5,Cremains
OL,7,FOn Tuesday, a senior Iranian commander
OL,8,Fwarned neighbouring Arab countries to
OL,9,F"say goodbye to oil production in the
OL,10,FMiddle East" if they allow the US to
OL,11,Fresume attacking Iran from their
OL,12,Fterritory.
OL,14,FSince the war started, fighting has
OL,15,Fkilled at least 3,375 people in Iran
OL,16,Fand more than 2,290 in Lebanon. Twenty-
OL,17,Fthree people have died in Israel and
OL,18,Fmore than a dozen in Gulf Arab states.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
